<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Fairways</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">From spacious villas to large, elegant bungalows, the real estate in Fairways includes homes suited for both families and singletons. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Many of the houses in this community are show homes and they have been maintained in a wonderful way. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Single and multi-story houses abound in Fairways. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The houses are designed juxtaposing both classical and contemporary architectural designs. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Some of the homes come fully furnished with baths and furniture. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">This peaceful neighborhood is renowned for its old and beautiful churches. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">There are also restaurants, cafes, pubs and movie theaters here.</p>
        </div>
